SELECT `colors`.`name`,`rgb`.`id`,`rgb`.`r`,`rgb`.`g`,`rgb`.`b` ,`hsv`.`h`,`hsv`.`s`,`hsv`.`v`
    FROM `rgb`,`colors`,`hsv`
    WHERE (`rgb`.`r` < 51 + 3 AND `rgb`.`r` > 51 - 3) 
    AND (`rgb`.`g` < 52 + 3 AND `rgb`.`g` > 52 - 3) 
    AND (`rgb`.`b` < 50 + 3 AND `rgb`.`b` > 50 - 3) 
    AND `rgb`.`id` = `colors`.`id` AND `hsv`.`id` = `rgb`.`id`

SELECT `colors`.`name`,`rgb`.`id`,`rgb`.`r`,`rgb`.`g`,`rgb`.`b` ,`hsv`.`h`,`hsv`.`s`,`hsv`.`v`
    FROM `rgb`,`colors`,`hsv`
    WHERE (`rgb`.`r` < 196 + 8 AND `rgb`.`r` > 196 - 8) 
    AND (`rgb`.`g` < 175 + 8 AND `rgb`.`g` > 175 - 8) 
    AND (`rgb`.`b` < 77 + 8 AND `rgb`.`b` > 77 - 8) 
    AND `rgb`.`id` = `colors`.`id` AND `hsv`.`id` = `rgb`.`id`
